OL,7,F"My heart sank." This is how Abi Lloyd
OL,8,FRoberts describes how she felt after a
OL,9,Fcolleague in the Welsh Ambulance
OL,10,Fservice, who took the call the night
OL,11,Fher brother died, told her that there
OL,12,Fhad been a fatal collision on the
OL,13,Foutskirts of
OL,15,FOn 2 June 2023 Abi's brother, Joshua
OL,16,FLloyd Roberts, 19, died while walking
OL,17,Fhome on the A4085, Ffordd Waunfawr,
OL,18,FCaeathro near Caernarfon.
