OL,7,FOn the same night, Abi, 25, was
OL,8,Fworking for the ambulance service,
OL,9,Fanswering 999 calls.
OL,11,FAbi's colleague received a call just
OL,12,Fafter 23:00 reporting a collision that
OL,13,Fhad happened on the road her brother
OL,14,FJosh was planning to walk home on.
OL,16,FAfter hearing about the call Abi felt
OL,17,Fsomething was not right. She asked
OL,18,F'what's happened? Who?'
