OL,7,FAlthough Abi did not know for certain
OL,8,Fthat Josh was the person who had died,
OL,9,Fshe had a strong feeling that
OL,10,Fsomething was wrong, and left work
OL,11,Fearly as she was so worried.
OL,13,FShortly after she arrived at her home
OL,14,Fin Caernarfon, confirmation came from
OL,15,Fthe police that Josh had died.
OL,17,F"I've never screamed so much in my
OL,18,Flife. Because I knew it was Josh, I
OL,19,Fjust needed someone to confirm it was
OL,20,Fhim.
