OL,7,F"But I knew from the moment the call
OL,8,Fcame in, and I don't know how, but I
OL,9,Fknew," said Abi.
OL,11,FJosh was originally from Caernarfon,
OL,12,Fand a student at Cardiff Metropolitan
OL,13,FUniversity.
OL,15,FHe was a talented footballer who
OL,16,Fplayed for his university team,
OL,17,FBontnewydd and Caernarfon Town. He was
OL,18,Falso an avid fan of Everton and Wales.
OL,20,F"He loved Everton. Football was his
OL,21,Freligion so to speak," said Abi.
