OL,7,F'I really miss him'
OL,9,FJosh and Abi were great friends and
OL,10,Fhis death has been devastating to
OL,11,Feveryone who knew him.
OL,13,F"I wake up every morning and hope it's
OL,14,Fnot true. I look at my phone every
OL,15,Fmorning and see his picture and then I
OL,16,Fremember. It's horrible, I miss him so
OL,17,Fmuch.
OL,19,F"He'll be 19 forever."
