OL,5,Ccalls
OL,7,FAfter Josh's death, Abi was offered
OL,8,Fpsychological help by her workplace,
OL,9,Fbut eight months after losing her
OL,10,Fbrother, she has decided to leave the
OL,11,Fambulance service and is now working
OL,12,Felsewhere.
OL,14,F"I feel like I'm stuck in time, I'm
OL,15,Fnot going back to my work, I have
OL,16,FPTSD, I'm afraid that something like
OL,17,Fthat is going to happen again."
